<subSubSection id="C368652E93538E0EF2AAF90AFE56F931" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2AAF90AFE56F931" blockId="10.[151,1437,1688,2038]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793538E0EF028F90AFDADF979" box="[533,636,1688,1714]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a female bearing a white label with “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF679F90BFB4BF979" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[1092,1178,1689,1714]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exiguus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF679F90BFB4BF979" box="[1092,1178,1689,1714]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">exiguus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
mihi in Gallia merid.” (these words are followed by an illegible word) and a red label “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793538E0EF1BAF92EFC2BF91D" box="[903,1018,1724,1750]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF618F92EFA4DF91D" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[1061,1436,1724,1750]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exiguus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF618F92EFB2AF91D" box="[1061,1275,1724,1750]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Acupalpus exiguus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF739F92EFA4DF91D" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1284,1436,1724,1750]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by J. Serrano”.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93538E0EF2FAF896FEEEF819" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAF896FD16F841" blockId="10.[151,1437,1688,2038]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
The original material was diverse. Of these beetles I have selected that one collected in South 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593538E0EF6D9F897FAE5F8D4" box="[1252,1332,1797,1823]" name="France" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">France</collectingCountry>
. It shows a dorsal dark colouration including the appendages, a rather small body size (2.7 mm), the pronotum with rounded posterior angles, etc. (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF3AEF8DEFDE2F8AD" author="Jeannel, R." box="[403,563,1868,1894]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel, 1942</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF07DF8DFFD03F8AD" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[576,722,1868,1895]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="344 - 386" refId="ref12516" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2004) Harpalina. In: Freude, H., Harde, K. W., Lohse, G. A. &amp; Klausnitzer, B. (Eds.), Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Bd. 2 Adephaga 1: Carabidae (Laufkafer). Spektrum-Verlag, Heidelberg / Berlin, pp. 344 - 386." type="book chapter" year="2004">Wrase, 2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF0E3F8DEFCCBF8AD" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[734,794,1868,1894]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
). These characters separate this species from 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF71EF8DEFEA5F841" authority="(Duftschmid, 1812)" baseAuthorityName="Duftschmid" baseAuthorityYear="1812" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="luteatus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF71EF8DEFA4CF8AD" box="[1315,1437,1868,1894]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">A. luteatus</emphasis>
(Duftschmid, 1812)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF397F8E2FD12F841" authority="Schilsky, 1888" authorityName="Schilsky" authorityYear="1888" box="[426,707,1904,1930]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dubius">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF397F8E2FDC4F841" box="[426,533,1904,1930]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">A. dubius</emphasis>
Schilsky, 1888
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAF806FEEEF819" blockId="10.[151,1437,1688,2038]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
The species is found from West Siberia and 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593538E0EF081F806FCEEF865" box="[700,831,1940,1966]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
to West 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593538E0EF19EF807FC3EF864" box="[931,1007,1941,1967]" name="France" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">France</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF1C2F806FAD7F865" author="Jaeger, B. &amp; Kataev, B. M." box="[1023,1286,1940,1967]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="1837" refId="ref10991" refString="Jaeger, B. &amp; Kataev, B. M. (2017) Subtribe Stenolophina Kirby, 1837. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 562 - 577." type="book chapter" year="2017">Jaeger &amp; Kataev, 2017</bibRefCitation>
), as noted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF2AAF82AFEEAF819" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[151,315,1976,2002]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
